data.description: Come home and relax in this cozy 3-2-2 home. High ceilings and a fireplace make this living area feel like home. The upgraded 18 in. ceramic tile throughout the home is usually found in higher priced properties. Want a low maintenance home? The seller has already done some painting inside and new roof shingles will be installed before closing. The exterior was repainted approx. 2 yrs ago and the privacy fence replaced approx. 5 yrs ago. The back yard has a lot of space. The kitchen has a pass thru to the family room making the home great for entertaining. All bedrooms and the living room have ceiling fans. The seller has done paint touchups inside and the home shows well. The home can be ready for a quick move in. The home is near schools and shopping. It is very close to the new HEB Plus on Bandera and 1604 and a short drive to the La Cantera Mall. Sea World is 7 miles away and Six Flags-Fiesta Texas is 10 miles away. This is a great starter home with affordable monthly payments. Ask
